parameters: Don't say someone's name like a traitor! My name is Hikaru!
Did you do it on purpose!?
Is this their own kind of joke?
It's a pattern that I've seen in an old story before.
Well... is there something you need help with?
You came at just the right time. So, um...
Can you help me pick up some firewood?

It seems that the gas is out due to the typhoon, so we
have to cook with firewood.

By the way, I thought it was strange to see pots and pans
here even though there's a kitchen. But it turns out
that the gas is out.

The gas ran out? Are you okay? It won't suddenly explode,
right?

Maybe it's not that the gas ran out in this house, but it
seems like a pipe broke somewhere else.
At least around here, there's no smell of gas.
If you have another job to do... that's okay.
How much firewood should I pick up?
Please just grab what firewood you can.

It's heavy... There's no need for you to go through the
trouble of bringing it without any reason.

They're saying that if you don't pick up a sufficient amount,
Tsugumi will end up having to go through the trouble
again.
Let's pick up as much as we can and bring it back.

If there are tree branches that can be used as
firewood...
I think there were a lot of them at the Survival field.
Oh... You brought a lot with you.
This is nothing much. Is there anything else you need?
Hmm, well then, could you bring the food, please?

I feel like the food will get cold if I go back and
forth by myself...

I can sense that she is happy now, although her change
in facial expression is unusual.
Her faint smile was very cute and endearing.

I am reminded of the words 'like a doll' that we were
talking about in the department.
Ah, yeah! Is this what I'm bringing?

No, this is just getting started... it's just water.
Could you come a little later?

I wanted to know more about Tsugumi. That's what I
thought.
...Perhaps there's something you want to eat?
It may not be enough, but... I'll give it my best shot.
What's the matter? You can always count on me!

The firewood was running around everywhere, it was tough,
but this should be enough, right?
Yes... Thank you, Hikaru. Is there something you want to eat?

Eh, Tsugumi's cooking is always abundant and it's
difficult to choose.
I wonder what would be good for dinner tonight...

Oh, the king of firewood, a new existence that conjures
forth new firewood...
Ah, I see. I completely understand.

Hey, if I become the king of firewood, I'll just end up
being burned and dying, right?
Ah, is that so? Well then, in that case...
No, no, you don't have to force yourself to make me laugh.
Then, kiss me on the cheek.
This time, some of firewood suddenly exploded...

...No, there is a more serious situation here... Did we
have to do a ritual or something...
Ah, don't just say that, it's wierd!
Hehe... Are you feeling pent up? What should we do...
Please come to my room tonight.
Or should I come to you instead?
Hehe... Well, I have a little something to take care of...
Ah, could it be... a rabbit?

No, I thought I couldn't catch it... It was getting away
, but suddenly fell asleep.

I don't expect her to jump for joy,
but she's happier than I thought.

Well, as the person who caught it,
I'm glad to see her happy about it.
By the way, how do you cook and eat rabbits?
Should we try grilling it randomly?
That's fine, isn't it? There's still pepper left too.

We made grilled rabbit and surprised everyone at the dinner
table.

The amount of food per person was small because there were
many people, but everyone happily ate it, saying It's
like MAN VS. WILD!
The taste... was just like the taste of bland chicken.
Hikaru! I want to eat rabbit meat!
Rabbit! I want to eat it!

It's a chance to earn points with me, the super beautiful
Kanae-sama, you know?
Oh, so that's how you're approaching it.
So, are you going to do it this time too?
Umm, I wonder what will happen~

W-Well, it's not like I'll be specifically waiting for
you or anything...
I-It's nothing! Just catch one already!
Yes, yes. If it's the princess's wish, then by all means.
Oh~ I'm searching for delicious meat~ I hate eating grass~
...Eh, what's with that song... Hikaru, you're cool.
Ah, it's Hikaru! Did you succeed?

The level of the rabbit was far too weak. It's so
boring, I felt like dying.
...You're saying things that I don't understand, but...
Hunting for me... is the same as murder...
What are you saying, keep saying weird things...

Don't you read any manga or anything... It's even worse than
Tsugumi.
Eh, was that a line from a manga?
I thought you hit your head somewhere.
How can you not know this famous line...!
Hehe, well done! Should we roast it again this time?

I checked the refrigerator, and it seems that there are
still ingredients prepared by Tsugumi from yesterday.
Let's make soup and eat it this time.
Rabbit soup~ Sounds good. I'm looking forward to it.
The rabbit soup turned out, as expected, tasting normal.

I think it's impressive that even beginners can make it
normally...
Are you setting up the antenna?

It seems that the sight of Kenta-senpai sweating
profusely indicates that he was very focused.
I'm sorry if I'm bothering you.
No, no, you're not bothering me at all.

Actually, it's different from what I tried before and I'm
hesitating.

Just because it's an antenna doesn't mean they're all the
same...
Is there anything I can help you with?

Ah, since I'm gripping the bottom tightly, could you push
it a little?
It seems that I have to insert it into this hole...

I slowly began to grip the end of the antenna and apply
pressure.
Huh? It's just going to come out like that.
Can you put a little more strength into it?
L-Let's try it one more time.

The antenna keeps slipping out as if it's spinning in
place.

The problem might be that I was too weak, but the strength
that enters my palm becomes even stronger.
If you put that much strength...

At that moment, with a loud cracking sound, the antenna
broke.
The two of us who end up speaking very little.
It seems that the signal is difficult to connect again.
There is a map depicting the area around the cottage.

I've memorized it to some extent, but should I confirm it
again?
A large capacity pot with a sturdy shape.
Wow... Did you catch another one?
Maybe I'm a genius at hunting...
If it wasn't for that, you would have been cool~

It would be nice if we could synchronize our words at
times like this...
No, well, it's not like that...
By the way~, there's also one in my room, a rabbit.
Did you originally want to try hunting or something?
Maybe they wanted to try it because I always succeed.

However, after catching it myself, I wanted to keep it... or
something like that.
Come to my room later. I'll show you.
Come to my room later. I'll show you something.
